{"tid":1986184,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底大學生應唔應該翻part time賺錢草錢？","createTime":"2020-04-23T16:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:15:13.000Z","uid":301809,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"13d6e3d67757520d7536ebb6fb8ad3bc69633997","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"自己考完DSE嗰下就開始翻part time，<br />\n入大學之後就reg哂下晏堂，朝早翻工下晏上堂，上完5點再幫2個學生私補，每日嘅生活就好似朝9晚6一樣。<br />\n<br />\n跟住由停課開始，補習學生需求大咗，又有唔同家長揾我幫佢地小朋友補習，去到依家有8個學生，每日起碼要連住補3個。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊暑假唔洗翻學，已經諗住去翻part time。<br />\n有時聽到自己啲fd日日冇野做，喺hall玩，拍拖等等，但又冇翻工冇草錢習慣，日日處於糧尾狀態借grant loan等等。跟住佢地就會好奇怪我點解可以草到錢啊嗰啲，點解唔拎啲時間去拍拖，同朋友出街食飯等等，以後大把苦等自己捱等等。<br />\n<br />\n但其實自己唔係咩拜金女，又唔會拎錢買名牌野，買過最貴嘅野畀自己應該係DW錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我純粹覺得大個女18歲唔應該再問屋企人畀錢自己洗，自己都係時候要有啲經濟能力草下錢等大個女可以冇咁辛苦，又可以減輕另一半負擔咁。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有人話大學生正職應該係讀書追first hon, 翻工應該係副業，畀自己有啲零用錢洗就夠，但我自己覺得大學生應該要開始熟習將來社會生活模式，翻下part time草下錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"eeb22382ac0fee25fce4ce3c9a6243e0bdecc61a","tid":1986184,"uid":238504,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"前提唔可以犧牲成績"},{"pid":"0c132408cf1d6648b662f3fb60bf9ef174cb8301","tid":1986184,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"最貴都只係DW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！"},{"pid":"14ee1d74a2aae47cc587bbb5879fb23bfce5b31d","tid":1986184,"uid":25260,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"當年都差唔多每日放學都私補，又住hall日日玩<br />\n2nd low 畢業，而家咪又係好地地"},{"pid":"3897d32115f9dd4b66a674cca8a060c06889d948","tid":1986184,"uid":233167,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"每個人都有自己生活，無話應唔應該"},{"pid":"73c983468b4b20f5b24ba83a000d24f666992feb","tid":1986184,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0c132408cf1d6648b662f3fb60bf9ef174cb8301","tid":1986184,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"最貴都只係DW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"好女仔，我中學暑期工已經買iphone9(嗰陣仲係5,6K一部)"},{"pid":"f4c25044ac3439f009da20dcd6506155f7daabb3","tid":1986184,"uid":275447,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"開頭我都覺得想自己得閒就幫人補習儲吓錢，平時就留喺屋企一日食兩餐，後尾發覺一個月儲得嗰幾千蚊，搞到自己日日都咁辛苦，使又唔捨得使，連學費都唔夠比，儲完都唔知為乜，開始想做返廢青了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515f9a467ae58993262f06cc7bb2277ec8143564","tid":1986184,"uid":134636,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"絕對要返pt，多個錢去買自己鍾意的野又好，儲下經驗又好，待人接物都好過剩係返學放學鳩fingfing <br />\n不過父幹撚或者好積極參加學校唔同活動另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec5d5e8fbd3e19daa5fa7495a3b9306cfc8a80d","tid":1986184,"uid":342281,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"借grant loan都可以唔洗問父母拎錢㗎 唔想用盡都可以儲起 畢業之後如果冇空檔期還錢都唔會好大壓力<br />\n同埋大學四年返pt嘅錢可能返正職幾個月已經追得上 何必咁辛苦逼啲時間出黎搵少少錢 不如趁求學階段有時間去接觸多啲嘢"},{"pid":"24da04f5ead04202af291da1d2f966a0c29b31b4","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eeb22382ac0fee25fce4ce3c9a6243e0bdecc61a","tid":1986184,"uid":238504,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"前提唔可以犧牲成績"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"呢個一定嘅，目前份份asm都早交，而讀嘅科又handle到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b0578fc92121213f359374803261c449bce624","tid":1986184,"uid":138802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73c983468b4b20f5b24ba83a000d24f666992feb","tid":1986184,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0c132408cf1d6648b662f3fb60bf9ef174cb8301","tid":1986184,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"最貴都只係DW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"好女仔，我中學暑期工已經買iphone9(嗰陣仲係5,6K一部)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"iphone9前幾日先出喳喎"},{"pid":"dc3cac7e9cebbb4ee3533aab14fabb08d5ab725f","tid":1986184,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b0578fc92121213f359374803261c449bce624","tid":1986184,"uid":138802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73c983468b4b20f5b24ba83a000d24f666992feb","tid":1986184,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0c132408cf1d6648b662f3fb60bf9ef174cb8301","tid":1986184,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"最貴都只係DW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"好女仔，我中學暑期工已經買iphone9(嗰陣仲係5,6K一部)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"iphone9前幾日先出喳喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"打多咗個9，想打( <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8ffa07565b4a65b62654116128e28190353c14","tid":1986184,"uid":134636,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"不過樓主講話要熟習將來社會生活模式不如試下揾返啱你major的pt，當然你話之後返intern都可以感受下，不過剩係做私補pt就揾錢成份多過熟習社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係都要留返d時間比自己做鍾意的野，year 1 2 我好努力打工3日返學4日，完全冇自己時間大壓力又爛gpa<br />\n<br />\nYear 3 4 揾到一份剩係返1日的文職pt，返3日學，多左時間去玩又好温書又好，心情輕鬆好多"},{"pid":"580ef9a73f0a767a8cbeac5f8f340053cabee098","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c132408cf1d6648b662f3fb60bf9ef174cb8301","tid":1986184,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"最貴都只係DW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰陣翻咗3個月工，草咗啲錢就決定買嚟獎勵自己"},{"pid":"62804e8c361ac7caa4d6e536a2ea1097f561acf3","tid":1986184,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"最好星期六返多三四個鐘餐廳識下仔"},{"pid":"fa3f2a58b4e19d68c544792487ddbc97ad00b807","tid":1986184,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"那有錢 你老母"},{"pid":"6d73db3c8fc00e655e636d11a3c9a0e007873393","tid":1986184,"uid":18411,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"過來人經驗<br />\n返工草錢係重要<br />\n不過趁住年輕該洗就要洗<br />\n多D去吓旅行，去exchange<br />\n洗錢唔係問題，但要洗得有意義<br />\n我畢業前草左10幾萬<br />\n如果有得揀重黎，我會多D去唔同地方探索吓個世界"},{"pid":"6793c751e1d56a4fe73e80cce60aa55f69c87265","tid":1986184,"uid":259373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"堂照上工照返<br />\n賺返啲零用錢同時儲下經驗<br />\n見到身邊個個都一份intern接一份 就唔敢唔返了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚grad咗先發現比人輸蝕"},{"pid":"63f1230d550777cea5261e44f6003da0def8dd6c","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c25044ac3439f009da20dcd6506155f7daabb3","tid":1986184,"uid":275447,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"開頭我都覺得想自己得閒就幫人補習儲吓錢，平時就留喺屋企一日食兩餐，後尾發覺一個月儲得嗰幾千蚊，搞到自己日日都咁辛苦，使又唔捨得使，連學費都唔夠比，儲完都唔知為乜，開始想做返廢青了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能係我啱啱入大學，未習慣呢種有day off ，冇咩workload嘅日子，可能過多2年我就唔會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76a3208e0cc1629324112b674bdf1bca5ab4249","tid":1986184,"uid":275447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63f1230d550777cea5261e44f6003da0def8dd6c","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c25044ac3439f009da20dcd6506155f7daabb3","tid":1986184,"uid":275447,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"開頭我都覺得想自己得閒就幫人補習儲吓錢，平時就留喺屋企一日食兩餐，後尾發覺一個月儲得嗰幾千蚊，搞到自己日日都咁辛苦，使又唔捨得使，連學費都唔夠比，儲完都唔知為乜，開始想做返廢青了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能係我啱啱入大學，未習慣呢種有day off ，冇咩workload嘅日子，可能過多2年我就唔會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"自己諗吓呢幾千蚊值唔值得搞到咁辛苦，可能求其補一兩個咪算囉，我而家補緊7堂都覺得幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n講真，補到咁辛苦，到頭來你得到啲乜？就算比你儲到錢，你夠錢買啲乜？"},{"pid":"bdde6e5a13cee3d9f5428963a1ac6044b8d00918","tid":1986184,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515f9a467ae58993262f06cc7bb2277ec8143564","tid":1986184,"uid":134636,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"絕對要返pt，多個錢去買自己鍾意的野又好，儲下經驗又好，待人接物都好過剩係返學放學鳩fingfing <br />\n不過父幹撚或者好積極參加學校唔同活動另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit